description: After arranging domestic/air logistics ship_booking for the integrated channel, use this API to get the tracking number, which is displayed separately for printing shipping labels

parameters.name: partner_id
parameters.description: Partner ID is assigned upon registration is successful

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: This is to indicate the timestamp of the request. Required for all requests. Expires in 5 minutes

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: This token for API access, using to identify your permission to the api, refer to /auth/token use and expires in 4 hours

parameters.name: shop_id
parameters.description: Shopee's unique identifier for a shop. Required param for seller API.

parameters.name: sign
parameters.description: Authentication parameter for partner_id, api path, timestamp, access_token, shop_id and partner_key via HMAC-SHA256 algorithm

parameters.name: booking_sn
parameters.description: Shopee's unique identifier for a booking

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: The identifier for an API request for error tracking

response_fields.name: error
response_fields.description: Indicate error type if hit error. Empty if no error happened

response_fields.name: message
response_fields.description: Indicate error details if hit error. Empty if no error happened

response_fields.name: tracking_number
response_fields.description: The tracking number of this booking
